{"type":"message","id":"3694ae42","parentId":"942527b5","timestamp":"2026-03-09T18:20:00.027Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-03-10 02:19 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 批量发布所有Skills到ClawHub\n\n使用API Token: clh_1fCyGAxj2bNgAqc3UmhZZJ9z4F0dbHAAVFlyzIEOPaA\n\n需要发布的Skills（35个）：\n1. 首先发布4个已有付费版的免费版：\n   - config-format-converter\n   - batch-file-renamer\n   - qr-code-tool\n   - rest-api-tester\n\n2. 然后发布其他31个待变现Skills\n\n每个Skill发布流程：\n1. 读取SKILL.md文件\n2. 调用ClawHub API: POST https://api.clawhub.com/v1/skills\n3. 记录发布结果（成功/失败）\n\nAPI调用格式：\n```bash\ncurl -X POST \"https://api.clawhub.com/v1/skills\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer clh_1fCyGAxj2bNgAqc3UmhZZJ9z4F0dbHAAVFlyzIEOPaA\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"name\": \"skill-name\",\n    \"content\": \"<base64-encoded-skill-md>\",\n    \"source\": \"github\",\n    \"visibility\": \"public\"\n  }'\n```\n\n发布完成后：\n1. 统计成功/失败数量\n2. 更新memory/skill-registry.json中的publishStatus\n3. 记录失败的Skills和原因\n4. 汇报每个成功发布的ClawHub URL\n\n注意：\n- 已有付费版的Skills发布免费版（有版本对比和Gumroad钩子）\n- 其他Skills发布完整功能版（待后续变现）\n- 如果API返回409 Conflict（已存在），视为成功并更新URL\n- 控制发布频率，避免被限流（每5秒一个）"}],"timestamp":1773080400020}}
{"type":"message","id":"8abe6c4b","parentId":"3694ae42","timestamp":"2026-03-09T18:20:03.238Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要批量发布35个Skills到ClawHub。让我先检查现有的skill-registry.json文件，了解有哪些Skills需要发布。\n\n首先，让我：\n1. 读取skill-registry.json了解当前状态\n2. 列出所有需要发布的Skills\n3. 按顺序逐个发布（每5秒一个）\n4. 记录结果并更新台账\n\n让我开始吧。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:0","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/memory/skill-registry.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /workspace/projects/workspace/skills/ | head -50","workdir":"/workspace/projects/workspace"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":7593,"output":136,"cacheRead":3328,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11057,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773080400026}}
